_sText:
This is a PURE custom texture map made by GabrielPapaK. It is a nice arena for any server. There is so much action is such a small room. Also symetrical so that no one can say its unfair...

Features:
-Custom Groovy Textures
-Symetrical Map

Install:
-Just export all the files (.bsp, .bak, .nav) to your map folder. Very easy.

Author:
-GabrielPapaK

Time:
-3 Hours

Hope You Enjoy!
